-- Lehman cuts exposure to leveraged loans
-- 
-- Thu Dec 13, 2007 10:52am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/12/13/us-lehman-loans-idUSWEN295920071213

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Lehman Brothers Holdings Inc LEH.N on Thursday said it had cut its exposure to leveraged loans by about two-thirds by the end of the fiscal fourth quarter from the end of the third. 

 Lehman said it had $9.8 billion in leveraged loan commitments at quarter-end, down from $27 billion at the end of the fiscal third quarter and down from $44 billion at the end of the second quarter. (Reporting by  Dane Hamilton , editing by Gerald E. McCormick)